snippet.textDisplay: This depicts the plight of bride's  family who are squeezed by societal pressures of mere show off and extravagance,a hallmark of Kashmiri marriage....But there is other side of the coin too...Many young kashmiri's have rejected and are rejecting the extravagant marriages and are saying clear NO to the dowry system.Both bride's and bridegroom's family are contributors of Societal evils in Kashmir but many are realising it though at a slow pace.
